name: Beings II
description: "It Awaits" - (SOUND ON) Driving along the snowy highway, he is on the verge of nodding off. These long roads are always quiet, and he knows the way like the back of his hand. He takes his eyes off the road for a second, for he knows he's safe. Then he turns his head back - and that's when he notices, something is not quite right. Up ahead, a glowing figure towers over the mountains.   /   Part 2 of a trilogy storyline.   /   Collector will have an option to receive a print.
